data.description: Timeless charm meets modern comfort with this one! This is a spacious 4 bedroom, 4 bathroom home with over 3,000 square feet! This home boasts large bedrooms as well a large family room downstairs that is perfect for entertaining. There is also a separate living quarters that has its own entrance which offers more space or the opportunity for extra income! On just over an acre, the backyard is an orchard oasis with tons of space, mature landscaping, and fruit trees! This home has a brand new roof that is warrantied for 50 years and new rain gutters. You will love the updates along with vintage appeal of the 1970s architecture so don't wait to come take a tour!
